## How to Run

### 1. Set up API keys
```bash
cd backend
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env and fill in:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# TAVILY_API_KEY=tvly-...
```

### 2. Install backend dependencies
```bash
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Start backend
```bash
cd backend
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000
```

### 4. Start frontend (separate terminal)
```bash
cd frontend
npm run dev
```

### 5. Open dashboard
Navigate to [http://localhost:3000/dashboard](http://localhost:3000/dashboard)

Try the sample keywords: `revenue intelligence`, `data warehouse cost optimization`, `AI in RevOps`
